reviewText: Im a huge fan of Bruce lee ive sawed it as a youngster

GREAT DVD OF GREEN HORNET EPISODES !! I purchased it for one episode in particular (Freeway to Death) which stars my FAVORITE guy Jeffrey Hunter. Great episode & the other 5 episodes are good too. Nice to purchase certain episodes w/o buying an entire season. But, If you're a fan, an entire season would be NICE. GREAT SELLER, SUPER FAST SHIPPING ALSO.
